WEBVTT

00:03:29.758 --> 00:03:33.536
because I was no geek,
I was no technology guy,

00:03:33.536 --> 00:03:36.295
and all the equipment needed
was already there,

00:03:36.295 --> 00:03:38.501
was easily available.

00:03:38.501 --> 00:03:41.617
And I realized that
we had a frontier here,

00:03:41.617 --> 00:03:43.080
a very important one,

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:46.237
that it was just a matter
of changing the perspective,

00:03:46.237 --> 00:03:48.466
and the web could be actually used,

00:03:48.466 --> 00:03:51.908
already used, as a colossal
and uncontrollable

00:03:51.908 --> 00:03:55.721
and highly anarchical TV channel,
TV network,

00:03:55.721 --> 00:04:00.905
and anyone with very basic skills
and very basic equipment,